name: Insurance Specialists
overview: Insurance Specialists is an independently owned Insurance agency and has been servicing Nevada and its residents since 2003. We are conveniently located at 5025 S Eastern Ave #20 in Las Vegas. We service Northern and Southern Nevada as well as the surrounding areas of Henderson, Summerlin, Boulder City, and North Las Vegas. We also service the surrounding states of Utah, California, and Arizona. Insurance Specialists prides itself on helping you and your family make an informed decision on all of your insurance needs. We specialize in Auto Insurance, Home Insurance, Commercial Business Insurance, Rental Property Coverage, Motorcycle, Boat, RV Insurance, and many other types of Insurance. We are proud to be “Signature Agents” for Progressive Insurance as well as agents for several other companies. Our goal is to help our clients find the best insurance with the best prices.
